{
  "style": "",
  "texts": [
    "The topics extracted by BERTTopic are described in terms of the most important words and their relevance.",
    "We interpreted them and assigned names to each cluster.",
    "In a next step, we computed for each sentence v the probability p v,z of belonging to each cluster z.",
    "We considered that a sentence v belongs to a cluster z if p v,z > 0.3 to allow for sentences to be categorized into at most three topics.",
    "We then grouped the sentences by participant y to obtain the set of topics Z y for their entire text answer."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}